info.description:
API collection for the Lodge Management System backend. Phase 1 + Phase 2 endpoints: Auth, Users, Rooms, Clients, Bookings, Password Policy, Workflow Engine.

Base URL: {{base_url}}
Set `token` variable after login — all authenticated requests use it automatically via collection auth.

